Package: mo.gov
Title: Missouri Open Data (Socrata SODA) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Missouri Open Data Socrata SODA API
    at data.mo.gov. Covers dataset listing, search, SoQL queries, and named
    functions for alcohol licenses, unemployment claims, state employee pay,
    expenditures, agriculture, public safety, health, education, employment,
    natural resources, and more. Includes LLM context injection via mog_context().
